      <title>美联储的通胀争论转向商品价格能下降多少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/fed-s-inflation-debate-shifts-to-how-much-goods-prices-can-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当美联储官员紧盯着其反通胀行动的最后一英里时，一个关键问题正变得越来越成为争论的核心：商品价格会继续下跌吗？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/fed-s-inflation-debate-shifts-to-how-much-goods-prices-can-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
